items.title: OtterBox iPhone 16 FRĒ Series Waterproof Case with MagSafe (Designed by LifeProof) - Sagebrush Green, Waterproof, 60% Recycled Plastic, Sleek and Stylish
items.description:
Product Description
Dive into the action with Frē Series. Originally designed and engineered by LifeProof, the Frē Series waterproof iPhone 16 case is sealed up, so you can submerge it to 2 meters for 1 hour. It covers your phone on all sides with an integrated screen cover and is rated to 5X military standard drop defenses to survive hard falls. Now, anchors are built-in so you can connect straps, and it snaps securely to MagSafe accessories. For easy Camera Control interaction, Frē Series has a silicone skin over the button that's touch sensitive, fully sealed and works with Apple's visual intelligence.

  


Specifications:




  


Compatible With:

  - iPhone 16



  


Drop Height:

  - DROP+ | 5X as many drops as military standard (MIL-STD-810G 516.6)



  


Dimensions:

  - 6.29 x 3.23 x 0.59 in | 15.98 x 8.20 x 1.51 cm



  


Weight:

  - 0.170952 lb | 77.543 g



  


Materials:

  - Polycarbonate Layer
  - Thermoplastic Elastomer
  - Thermoset Elastomer plug
  - MagSafe



  


Case Features:

  - Built-in magnets snap firmly to MagSafe chargers and accessories
  - WaterProof+ | WaterProof for 2 meters up to 1 hour | IP68
  - Built-in gaskets seal the case when snapped together
  - Pressure-fitted gasket protects charging ports
  - Built-in screen protector and port covers for 360 protection
  - Attach a lanyard or wristlet for added drop prevention
  - Works with 5G networks
  - Limited lifetime warranty supported by hassle-free customer service

About this item
- Perfect Fit for iPhone 16: Precision-engineered exclusively for the iPhone 16, this OtterBox case offers a flawless fit. It not only preserves your phone's sleek design but also ensures unparalleled protection against everyday hazards.
- Eco-Friendly Protective Case: Crafted with over 50% recycled plastic, including ocean-based materials, this case sets a new standard in protective innovation, safeguarding your phone and the planet.
- Unyielding OtterBox Defense: With an IP68 rating, our waterproof case offers complete security for any adventure. Enjoy DROP+ protection that's 5X stronger than military standards, ensuring your device remains pristine through every plunge and tumble.
- MagSafe & Wireless Charging Compatible: Discover seamless attachment with the OtterBox Frē Series case featuring built-in magnets, ensuring a strong lock to all MagSafe chargers and accessories for a worry-free experience.
- Trusted OtterBox Quality: With OtterBox, you're not just buying a case; you're investing in peace of mind. Our limited lifetime warranty covers material and workmanship defects, guaranteeing quality and exceptional customer service.

items.title: AeroGarden Mountain Meadows Flower Seed Pod Kit (7-pod)
items.description:
Product Description
Bring a blooming mountain meadow right into your home! A lush blend of lavender, pink, yellow, red, and white mountain meadow flowers – now you can bring the beauty of the outdoors in with this colorful collection. The Mountain Meadow Seed Kit includes dark pink Dianthus, yellow Coreopsis, yellow striped Gazania, and a colorful blend of Phlox. A vibrant collection of blooming flowers reminiscent of fresh, flowering meadows. Works in all AeroGardens. Planting with Seed Pods is fun and easy! Just insert the pre-seeded Grow Pods in your garden, add water and the patented, specially formulated Liquid Nutrients. Most plants germinate within 7-14 days, are ready for harvesting in 4-6 weeks, and will keep producing continuous harvests for up to 6 months and longer. Indoor gardening can’t get any simpler!

About this item
- The Mountain Meadow 7-Pod Seed Kit includes 7 pre-seeded pods, featuring: dark pink Dianthus (1), yellow Coreopsis (2), yellow striped Gazania (2), and a mix of Phlox (2)
- 100-Percent Germination Guarantee - if a Seed Pod doesn't germinate, we'll replace it for free
- No herbicides. No pesticides.
- Also includes a 3 oz bottle of patented, specially formulated Liquid Nutrients and a Growing Guide with step by step instructions
- For use in all AeroGardens

items.title: Merrell Men's Sneaker
items.description:
Product Description
The Outside is more than just a place. Merrell knows that. It's in their DNA, their history and the inspiration for their future. What started as a one-man boot making operation in 1981 has become a global calling to get outside and get moving. Beloved by backpackers and hikers, Merrell blazed trails, creating lighter, more comfortable footwear. Evolutions in design and technology allowed runners and hikers access to multi-sport and cross-training products designed to help them go farther, faster. Thirty years later, Merrell continues to innovate new technologies focused to get you outside, to keep you moving. Get ready to take the scenic route with Merrell.

Simple, comfy and casual - the Jungle slip-on from Merrell is a perfect fit. The smooth leather upper keeps things presentable and the elasticized panels deliver a flexible, snug fit and feel. The Jungle Runner sticky rubber outsole has excellent grip across changing terrain while the Air Cushion midsole allows long-wearing comfort.

A soft engineered jacquard mesh upper comfortably wraps your foot while supplying advanced ventilation. Additionally, the knit tongue and collar help provide a soft and supportive feel. items.title: PetSafe Adjustable Martingale Collar - Improves Leash Manners - Escape Prevention - Gentle Behavior Training - Durable Nylon - Alternative to Choke Collar - Petite 3/8" - Raspberry Pink
items.description:
Product Description
Walking your dog should be a stress-free experience, and the PetSafe Adjustable Martingale Collar is designed to make that possible. This innovative collar is an ideal solution for pet parents looking for more control without sacrificing comfort or safety. Unlike traditional choke collars, the PetSafe Martingale Collar uses a limited-slip design that only tightens when needed, preventing accidental escapes and discouraging pulling in a gentle, humane way. This makes it an excellent choice for gentle behavior training and improving leash manners. Made with premium nylon, the PetSafe Martingale Collar is both strong long lasting and lightweight for daily wear. Its martingale loop design provides gradual pressure rather than harsh corrections, which helps stop gagging and prevents injury to your dog’s neck and throat. It’s a comfortable alternative to a choke collar for dogs that need extra security during walks, especially those who tend to slip out of standard collars. The adjustable fit ensures that this collar can be tailored to your dog’s size for maximum safety and a secure fit. With easy to put on off functionality, this collar makes preparing for walks quick and convenient. Since 1988, PetSafe has been driven by a simple belief: safe, healthy pets lead to happier lives for pets and their families. For over 25 years, we've been dedicated to enhancing the lives of pets and the people who love them, treating every pet as a cherished family member and delivering life-changing innovations designed to enrich every moment. With U.S. roots and a global reach, our vet- and trainer-recommended products are built for every pet and backed by exceptional customer support. From backyards to dog parks, we're on a mission to create fields of joy for happy, healthy, and safe pets.

About this item
- Safe & Effective Control: The PetSafe Adjustable Martingale Collar provides better pet control and an escape prevention collar design for confident walking and training
- Comfortable Alternative: This no choke collar offers a comfortable soft fit with a martingale loop design that applies gentle, even pressure for safe redirection
- Built for Everyday Use: Crafted from strong long lasting nylon, this lightweight collar is easy to put on off and ideal for gentle behavior training during walks
- Global Mission, Local Care: With U.S. roots and worldwide reach, PetSafe delivers vet- and trainer-recommended solutions and exceptional customer support to create fields of joy for pets
- 25 Years of Trust: Since 1998, PetSafe has created safe, innovative, and trusted products that bring joy, enhance pet lives, and support the lifelong bond between pets and their families

additional_information.included components: petsafe martingale collar with quick snap buckle

items.title: Moen UTS2202EPBN Doux Collection M-CORE 2-Series 1-Handle Shower Trim Kit, Valve Required, Brushed Nickel
items.description:
Product Description
M-CORE is shower design on your time. This universal valve system is simpler and faster to install, and offers additional functionality with desired style choices to create an ideal shower environment. Moen has conducted extensive research to create M-CORE, and what drives the design is a passion to make the workday more streamlined for plumbers, and to give more freedom in showering functionality and design for both new construction and remodel projects. Homeowners and designers will enjoy M-CORE's improved style and finish options, including perfectly matching mixing and transfer trim, and refined details that provide the finishing touches to a dream bathroom. Once installed, M-CORE valves, with new 2-Series trim, have pressure-balancing capabilities designed to control temperature fluctuations in the event of water pressure changes in the home.

About this item
- WARM AND INVITING: Brushed Nickel finish provides a lightly brushed warm-grey metallic look
- VALVE REQUIRED: This trim kit requires M-CORE Mixing Valve U140, with preferred installation option, to complete installation
- PRESSURE-BALANCING CAPABILITY: M-CORE universal valves, with 2-Series trim, provide simple cycling between cold and hot temperatures, offering pressure-balancing capabilities designed to control temperature fluctuations in the event of water pressure changes in the home
- VERSATILE DESIGN: M-CORE’S adaptability allows the valves to be roughed-in with the option of functionality and style changes that don't require removing or changing the valve
- STREAMLINED INSTALLATION: Features an integrated mounting bracket that secures the valve directly to a brace, streamlining the installation process and saving time
- INTEGRATED TEST CAP: Offers a precise temperature limit stop adjustment, and the integrated test cap allows installers to easily flush and test the system without having to remove or install the cartridge
- BUILT TO LAST: Backed by Moen’s Limited Lifetime Warranty

additional_technical_details.included components: 1212 mixing valve cartridge, temperature limit stop, trim kit
